  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>\"Oh why bother\"</em></p><h5 id=\"-strong-benefit-strong-br-\"><strong>Benefit:</strong></h5><p>You have a knack for taking the wind out of other people's sails. Once per short rest, when you would see a creature gain advantage you may prevent that creature from gaining that instance of advantage.</p><h5 id=\"-strong-negative-strong-\"><strong>Negative:</strong></h5><p>Your negative attitude offen stops you from working at your full potential. At the beginning of each session roll a d20. If you roll an 8 or lower you do not start the session with a Will of Fire point.</p>",
